\f2\b0  \'96 the formal 
\f5\i dokusan
\f2\i0  (also called 
\f5\i sanzen
\f2\i0  or 
\f5\i mond\uc0\u333 
\f2\i0 ) became institutionalized in the 13th
\f3 \uc0\u8239 
