\f0\b Ask a probing question
\f2\b0  (\'93What does the word \'91Mu\'92 mean to you right now?\'94). \'95 
\f0\b Offer a direct pointing
\f2\b0  (\'93When you hear \'91Mu,\'92 let the sound dissolve into the space of your breath.\'94). \'95 
